### Test without token (should return 401)
GET {{ez_todo_api_HostAddress}}/api/todo
###

### List all todos (with token)
GET {{ez_todo_api_HostAddress}}/api/todo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Create a new todo
POST {{ez_todo_api_HostAddress}}/api/todo
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Pass the interview",
  "description": "Build backend and frontend"
}
###

### Update the todo (with token)
PUT {{ez_todo_api_HostAddress}}/api/todo/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "description": "Build backend, frontend and infrastructure"
}
###

### Toggle completion status
PATCH {{ez_todo_api_HostAddress}}/api/todo/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get a todo by id
GET {{ez_todo_api_HostAddress}}/api/todo/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Delete a todo
DELETE {{ez_todo_api_HostAddress}}/api/todo/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
